yet achievable goals

00:51:34.990 --> 00:51:37.240
for the two largest
economies, the two largest

00:51:37.240 --> 00:51:39.640
emitters of CO2.

00:51:39.640 --> 00:51:43.215
And it was a clear
positive step forward.

